Net-Dev-Tools-SyslogMessage version 1.01
========================================

Pure-Perl Unix Syslog message parser.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module does not require modules and libraries.

